<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4577399>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 7. A–D, habitus and structures of Scelidocteus incisus (Tullgren, 1910), new combination, male lectotype; E–G, habitus and structures of Scelidocteus incisus (Tullgren, 1910), new combination, female paralectotype; A, E, habitus in dorsal view; B, F, cephalothorax, dorsal; C, D, distal sclerites of palp, retrolateral and ventral view, respectively; G, cephalothorax in ventrolateral view. Scale bar = 1 mm (A, E); 0.5 mm (B, F, G); 0.1 mm (C, D)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4577399/files/figure.png" .

